==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: shàng qióng bìluò xià huángquán

===Etymology===
A quote from the ''Song of Eternal Sorrow'' ([[长恨歌]]), by [[wikipedia:Bai_Juyi|Bai Juyi (白居易)]].

Literally: (Searched) thoroughly up in the blue beyond (as well as) down in the Yellow Springs (below the earth).

===Idiom===
'''[[上]][[穷]][[碧落]][[下]][[黄泉]]'''

# Search high and low.
#: ''[[那个]][[在]][[美]][[军]][[攻占]][[巴格达]][[之]][[时]][[悄然]][[蒸发]]，[[让]][[十]][[数]][[万]][[大军]][[在]][[长]][[达]]8[[个]][[月]][[时间]][[里]]"'''上穷碧落下黄泉'''，[[两]][[处]][[茫茫]][[皆]][[不]][[见]][[的]]"[[的]][[萨达姆]]，[[却]][[一直]][[像]][[幽灵]][[一般]][[困扰]][[着]][[占领]][[当局]].''[http://72.14.235.104/search?q=cache:vbjCFdY1QggJ:www.people.com.cn/GB/guandian/1033/2247191.html+%22%E8%AE%A9%E5%8D%81%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%87%E5%A4%A7%E5%86%9B%E5%9C%A8%E9%95%BF%E8%BE%BE8%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E9%87%8C%22&hl=zh-CN&gl=cn&ct=clnk&cd=1]
#: '' [[wikipedia:Saddam Hussein|Saddam]] had disappeared into thin air shortly after the American forces took [[Baghdad]].  For eight months, he caused hundreds of thousands of soldiers to '''search high and low''', but was no where to be found.  Despite this, he continued to haunt the occupation authorities like a phantom.''

